Registered to vote? Here's a list of voter registration deadlines by state
  
 Election Day is just over a month away, so if you want to vote and you're not yet registered, you should figure out how to register before it's too late. Things are particularly urgent if you live in one of the red states on the above map — their deadlines range from October 4 to October 7, so they're right around the corner.  Below is the specific list of deadlines for each state, with links to state websites that have more information on how to get registered. Get our newsletter in your inbox twice a week. 